unreleased

And next  is the Apology#1. The Apology #2 is on a official release, the COmplete Hank Williams. Apology#1 is not. In the liner nots for the box set it clearly states a Apology was recorded for Baltimore and that is Apology #1. Apology#2 which was one the box set was tapped for Washington DC. Please enjoy these.
